folder: Broadway & north from Mosholu Ave., Bronx, NY
original_title: Bronx: Broadway - north from Mosholu Ave.
text:
Broadway, north from and including Mosholu Ave., showing, on the right, Van Cortlandt Park, and on the left, at the S.W. corner of the two thoroughfares, the Mosholu Inn. It was later known as Becker's Inn.

About 1917.
